        "setup": "In Ghost Admin, create a new `Custom Integration` from the **Integrations** screen and copy the Admin API key. This secret key is then used server-side to generate short-lived JWTs for requests. The docs describe this under token authentication and note that keys for individual users can also be found on their profile page: [Admin API overview](https://docs.ghost.org/admin-api) and [Admin API JavaScript client](https://docs.ghost.org/admin-api/javascript).",
